text: Gimnazija Šentvid (/ɡimnaziya ʃɛntvid/) is a secondary school in Šentvid district of Ljubljana, Slovenia. "Gimnazija" can be translated from Slovenian as high school or secondary school. The astronomical group of Gimnazija Šentvid and the Astronomical Society Vega - Ljubljana cooperate. ==External links== *Gimnazija Šentvid official website *Location of Gimnazija Šentvid on google maps Category:Secondary schools in Slovenia Category:Schools in Ljubljana
